                              XCONQ NEWS

This is release 5.5 of XConq.  Mail bug/questions/problems to

Emergency-saves are now performed again, when the game crashes.
You can 'S'ave the current game without terminating it.
Tiny bugfix in command.c, checking reference of NIL-Pointer

New functionalities: - Max. Round-Time settable via -T <minutes>
                     - ^W wake units of specified type only.

(Mail caronni@nessie.cs.id.ethz.ch for bugreports)
